org.dcm4che.data

Class Attributes

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.dcm4che.data.Attributes
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public class Attributes
extends Object
implements Serializable
    Provides classes for reading and writing components of Dicom objects.

    Dicom objects are composed of a set of elements, which each have an identifying tag (32 bit integer) and a value. The method for reading the value of the element is specified by the value representation of the tag VR.

    Author:
    Gunter Zeilinger
